neration. We aim to serve as a shoulder to stand on, an experience to learn from, as wisdom to pass on. Here <strong>we</strong> project <strong>our</strong> passions and clue our readers in to what inspires <strong>us</strong> in this crazy world. Join us on journey as we explore the myriads of identities, trends, cultures, and experiences that the world has in store for us.','Børn Great','','inherit','closed','closed','','43-revision-v1','','','2019-07-09 02:41:46','2019-07-09 02:41:46','',43,'http://born-great.local/2019/07/09/43-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
