INSERT INTO `_WPI_posts` VALUES (146,3,'2019-07-26 21:33:51','2019-07-26 21:33:51','<img class=\"wp-image-124 size-medium aligncenter\" src=\"http://born-great.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/borngreat-logos_bg_logo_blk-hor-300x116.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"116\">\n\nBørn Great is more than just a collaborative effort. Børn Great is a culmination of the cultures and identities that were handed down to us intermingled with the new identities that we are passionate about. It serves as a platform for self-expression, support, and catharsis.\n\n<em>Børn Great?... Yeah, right. In this life we have to struggle and prove our worth.</em>\n\nBørn Great can sounds pretty pompous from the moment you hear it. But, hear me out. We are the product of all the past experiences of the lineage that came before us. All the mistakes, triumphs, and even the mundane moments that we even find ourselves in from time to time. Those all had influence on us in one way or another and the amazing thing is— we are here. We are living in a time where barriers and limits are being pushed and broken more than ever. We were born to make change, to test the status quo, to live up to the countless dreams and aspirations that came before us. We were born to forge our own path, to learn, and to grow. <strong>We are all born with the potential to accomplish anything and that’s what makes us GREAT</strong>.\n\n<em>nanos gigantum humeris insidentes</em>&nbsp; - <em>we stand on the shoulders of giants</em>\n\nWe have access to wisdom that spans until what seems like the inception of humanity. In the age we live in, all this information is available to us after a few taps into a search engine. We are born with the opportunity to grow from the wisdom from those who came before us, master that wisdom, and push its boundaries. Børn Great aims to connect thinkers and creatives so that we can push the boundaries together and <strong>aspire to inspire </strong>the next generation. We aim to serve as a shoulder to stand on, an experience to learn from, as wisdom to pass on. Here <strong>we</strong> project <strong>our</strong> passions and clue our readers in to what inspires&nbsp;<strong>us</strong> in this crazy world. Join us on journey as we explore the myriads of identities, trends, cultures, and experiences that the world has in store for us.','Børn Great','','inherit','closed','closed','','43-revision-v1','','','2019-07-26 21:33:51','2019-07-26 21:33:51','',43,'http://born-great.local/2019/07/26/43-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
